[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ukuma Ta'ai: Huddersfield Giants forward signs two-year contract extension

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Huddersfield Giants forward Ukuma Ta'ai has signed a two-year contract extension.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 29-year-old Tongan, who joined the Giants from New Zealand Warriors in September 2012, was ever-present in the 2016 season.
"I am so excited that the club has given me the opportunity to stay," Ta'ai told the club website.
"The fans are fantastic and I am excited to be given the chance to stay here for another two years."
